    <item>
      <title>The social break (update) and a farewell</title>
      <link>https://larry.wapnitsky.com/posts/2025/social-break-farewell/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Feb 2025 05:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://larry.wapnitsky.com/posts/2025/social-break-farewell/</guid>
      <description>
         &lt;![CDATA[&lt;img src=&#34;%!s(&lt;nil&gt;)&#34;/&gt; ]]/&gt; 
         &lt;p&gt;I&amp;rsquo;m breaking my streak so that I can post this on social media, but this is most likely my last post on Facebook.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;The past month without using social media has actually been a mixed blessing. On one side, I&amp;rsquo;ve not been distracted by the apps (Facebook, Instagram, etc.) and their high levels of noise. I&amp;rsquo;ve also found myself taking more time to read and pursue more relaxing things to do in my downtime.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;One downside I&amp;rsquo;ve noticed is that I&amp;rsquo;ve missed interaction with many people with whom I&amp;rsquo;ve created friendly relationships online.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;While the latter is very important to me, getting of social media takes precedence. That&amp;rsquo;s why, as of March 16, 2025, I will be deactivating my Facebook and Instagram accounts. That means that I will no longer have access to any chats via FB messenger, so the only ways you will be able to get a hold of me are:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Calling me&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Texting me&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Emailing me&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;    &#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;    &#xA;&#xA;&lt;a href=&#34;https://signal.org&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener noreferrer nofollow&#34;&gt;Signal Messenger&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;If you don&amp;rsquo;t have my contact info and want to stay in touch, you can shoot me a message via FB (I may or may not get it), or email &#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;    &#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;    &#xA;&#xA;&lt;a href=&#34;mailto:sendlarryamessage@gmail.com&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;mailto:SendLarryAMessage@Gmail.com&#34;&gt;SendLarryAMessage@Gmail.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/a&gt; and I&amp;rsquo;ll get back to you ASAP.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;In the meantime, stay tuned here and check in for updates. The best way to do that is to use an RSS reader. &#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;    &#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;    &#xA;&#xA;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.lifewire.com/what-is-an-rss-feed-4684568&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener noreferrer nofollow&#34;&gt;What&amp;rsquo;s that?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;    &#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;img class=&#34;img-fluid &#34;&#xA;        src=&#34;https://larry.wapnitsky.com/img/posts/2025/flipside-2800x1575.png&#34;&#xA;        &#xA;        &#xA;        srcset=&#34;https://larry.wapnitsky.com/img/posts/2025/flipside-576x324.webp 576w, https://larry.wapnitsky.com/img/posts/2025/flipside-768x432.webp 768w, https://larry.wapnitsky.com/img/posts/2025/flipside-992x558.webp 992w, https://larry.wapnitsky.com/img/posts/2025/flipside-1200x675.webp 1200w, https://larry.wapnitsky.com/img/posts/2025/flipside-1400x788.webp 1400w, https://larry.wapnitsky.com/img/posts/2025/flipside-2800x1575.webp 2800w&#34; sizes=&#34;100vw&#34;&#xA;        height=&#34;1575&#34;&#xA;        width=&#34;2800&#34;&#xA;        alt=&#34;image&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;iframe src=&#34;https://countingdownto.com/w4/B639c5Mj&#34; frameborder=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;position:fixed;left:0;bottom:0;margin:0!important;width:100%;height:3.5rem;z-index:1;background-color:#FF0000;background-image:linear-gradient(135deg, #FF0000, #800000);&#34;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&#xA;
      </description>
